  - optionText: What can you tell me about Pinehill?
    replyText: "It\u2019s a quiet village in the middle of the desert. We\u2019ve
      got two mills that provide flour for our baker, Jonas. There\u2019s also Thomas\u2019
      gym and Travis\u2019 gun store. We\u2019re not a big settlement, but we have
      everything we need to live."
