  - optionText: How did you become the leader of this village?
    replyText: I became the leader by chance. I found some pre-war ruins, fixed them
      up, and built the mills. Soon, other people started coming and setting up their
      own businesses. I made a deal with President Nixon, who accepted us into the
      Republic of Arkansas and sent guards to protect us.
